data.text: @HeadSpaceSpace1 @AngelTibbs Nope they’re hoping for the worst.. Have you not heard about their depopulation goal?

@AngelTibbs It is wrong to even call this 'experimental'. B/C in a real experiment you would be collecting post-injection data on each and every subject to determine effectiveness & safety. They aren't collecting any post-injection data. They are just jabbing people and hoping for the best.
